Game info:
SP!TE is a wave based survival game. The waves go up to 25!
If you can get to 26 you have beat one of the levels.
There are currently 7 levels to choose from. all sorts of ammo, health
and bomb spawns, and weapons to choose from throughout the maps.
Health does increase over time.
SP!TE is set in post apocalyptic times where nuclear war is going on
throughout the globe, with zombies and monsters coming at you from
everywhere!
Note: Keybindings are case sensitive in this game.
